HEADWORD: Martite
<hw>Mar"tite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>Mars</ets>,
<ets>Martis</ets>, the god Mars, the alchemical name of iron.]</ety>
<fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>Iron sesquioxide in isometric form, probably a
pseudomorph after magnetite.</def>⟦br⟧
